      @HI{{omoshiroi}}@KT{{dezain}}@HI{{no}}@KJ{{shoes}}@HI{{desune.}}
      @HI{{dokode}}@KJ{{buy}}@HI{{tta<strong>ndesuka</strong>.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      The design of your shoes is interesting. Where did you buy them?
  </td> </tr>
</table>
</ol>

<h2> Notes </h2>

<strong>@HI{{ndesuka}}</strong> can contain the speaker's surprise or suspicion or strong curiosity
and may therefore cause offence, It should be used with care.
<p></p>

<strong>@HI{{ndesu}}</strong> is not used to state a simple fact.

